<lb n="7" break="no"/>rulaku kūḍujītamu daśabaṁdānakuṁgā māḍalu 8 Ēkāki śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>vaiṣṇavulaku <unclear>cinna</unclear>lu 12 māṇikālaku māḍa 1 ci <unclear>9</unclear> Iṁ
